    "subtype": "vehicle",
    "text": "What appears to be a simple, if bulky, backpack conceals clockwork devices that can inflate two large balloons, carrying the backpack\u2019s wearer through the air for brief periods of time. In addition, propellers allow the pilot to move while airborne.",
